node.text: We can plan out our lives and be 1000% sure it’s going to go according to our plan...and sometimes it still doesn’t.  Maybe everything won’t turn out like we think it will, but it will all turn out like God intended it to. @foreverdiamondsny Thank you for your friendship. Your hard work on this beautiful piece deserves to be shared regardless.
